title: The Stars Are Now Scrubs, Plus: Is Borrowing Fantasy Players Fair? | The Dantasy Football Podcast
description:
Most of the highest-paid running backs in the league had terrible weeks. Who can we trust? (2:20) Plus, we break down the Rams’ 2019 plummet into a ravine before picking our streamers in a bye-filled Week 11 (26:30). Then we adjudicate the case of borrowing fantasy players on another edition of Fantasy Court (46:45)
Hosts: Danny Kelly, Danny Heifetz, and Craig Horlbeck
